sxkbl - simple X keyboard layout viewer
======================================


Requirements
------------
In order to build sxkbl you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (sxkbl is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install sxkbl
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running sxkbl
-------------
See the man page for details
